Fourth Department,

September, 1955*

(September 21, 1955) The People of the State of New York ex rel. Mariano Fili, Appellant, against Walter B. Martin, as Warden of Attica Prison, Respondent.

Not published with other decisions of Sept. 21, 1955, 286 App. Div. 985, and Nov. 16, 1955, 286 App. Div. 1143.— [Rep.

Motion to appeal as a poor person and for other relief denied on the ground that the papers fail to show merit to the appeal.
